Comment: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OPENING
Comment: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ENDING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be one dashing man, but to think he has such bad habits…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu is in the same year as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he hates vegetables and only eats instant food, he has an exceeding ghastly face that looks like it came from the dark side of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He picks on the weak and sucks up to the strong. He's lazy and a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul would have surely stayed unblemished had I not met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did you get the duplicate key?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've earned Jougasaki-san's trust, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You back-stabbing bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you move anything, make sure to put it back exactly where you found it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one serious clean freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why his girlfriend is like that instead of flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boor such as yourself whose mind is filled with sex probably couldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a form of extremely sophisticated love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H6C00C6&\fad(200,0)}J{\c&H000000&}-pwq
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student and before my eyes were held out innumerable circle fliers far surpassing my personal information intake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In each and every one of them I could see a door to that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one I chose was…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There I was sure to lay my future of pure, sparkling gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My new cinema paradise with raven-haired maidens dancing on the silver screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to join that day in order to make 100 friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,led astray by the naive words of\N "Let's have fun making movies together."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was truly an idiot beyond all redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HE3EAEA&}"Sincerity vs. Authority"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the movie circle "Misogi" which I joined that day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was under authoritarian rule by the president, Jougasaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HAEC2CC&}"Teacher and Student Go to War"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take 12, ready… Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H263741&\3c&HB7CBD4&\pos(160,27)}"Jougasaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H263741&\3c&HB7CBD4&\pos(832,27)}"I"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just not right yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout this! After the break, let me do another take.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit… To hell with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was annoyed with Jougasaki-senpai's meaningless productions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was then that an ominous man stood beside me with a face of ill portent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from the dark side of the moon? Or perhaps an E.T.?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say some pretty mean things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry, I am your compatriot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first contact with Ozu, as well as worst contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he does is parrot what he's read in 'how-to-make-movies' books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's Godard and Truffaut and the like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the all-time best is actually that Titanic guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to have a guy whose head is only filled with boobs run the movie circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Movies must definitely not be allowed to be poisoned by commercialism!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us a movie circle the way it should be, with your own two bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the purpose of raising the beacon of mutiny against Jougasaki-senpai's fiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started filming my own personal movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HEAEEE7&}"Approach"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first work: after the war in the Pacific, two men continue a battle of historic pranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,exhausting the limits of intelligence and physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A movie of overflowing war and violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was ignored and the only person in the theater that laughed was Akashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My second work: a sentimental movie about a man wavering between three women,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,patterned after King Lear.\N It received a storm of vilification from the women's camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my third work: a man trapped in a never-ending maze of 4.5 tatami rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his attempts to escape from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a DOA after people said "I've seen this premise before somewhere…"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,0)\c&HA6A8A7&}Youjo-han
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,0)\c&H2653B4&}"The - End"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahashi-san was the only one who gave me useful criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was odd was that I couldn't help but think that the more effort I put in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more Jougasaki-senpai's charisma seemed to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next work shall be Alexander the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will surely be a super grade-A piece of entertainment, the culmination of our work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, everyone… Will you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ablution!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think back on it now, I was used as leverage to increase his charismatic appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undaunted by Jougasaki-senpai, we attempted to announce a new romance film we were shooting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but his faction was unanimously against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's first line of attack was Aijima-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-senpai's right-hand man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who picked on us annoyingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using acrobatic tricks of the filming schedule and petty things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like turning off the electricity, hiding the key etc… He shut us out from the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end no one would deal with me, and I was shut out of the movie circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he be so celebrated while we have to resign ourselves to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now… The public is finicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they will always recognize a film that's true to itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when will that be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my recognition now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite selfish, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really so motivated, why do you have such a down-in-the-dumps look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I've wasted my perfectly lovely college life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I think you're to blame for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it doesn't matter which path you take, you'll keep ending up right where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we had this conversation before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. It's déjà vu, just déjà vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, once I met you I put all my efforts into making you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you haunt me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the way I show my love! We're connected by the black thread of fate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\c&HA567D6&}"The Japan Trench"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, here. This is Jougasaki-senpai's transcript.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a great face, but what's inside his head is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in his eighth year?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, his grades are dangerously low!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't underestimate my information-gathering network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to escape from this sad reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his heart has been more and more captured by the boobs of his female circle members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also the reason behind that last infamous swimsuit audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He filmed them in swimsuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no exhibitionism in the actual film.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly what made it so infamous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an aside, here are the marks from the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H213D40&\3c&HCCD1D0&\be4}"Name"  "Shape"  "Size"  "Remarks"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows the breasts' shape, angel, size, and separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely mixed up his private fetish with his public behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then he's just a boob dictator!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. In short, he's nothing but a boob junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a boob drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu! I have an idea. Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to leave the circle anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I at least want to bring down heavenly judgment on Jougasaki-senpai before the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, that's not very calm of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll follow you wherever you go, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus I was driven to action by my righteous indignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to throw cold water on the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or to put it simply, I decided to film an exposé documentary on Jougasaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save the underclassmen charmed by Jougasaki-senpai's meager charisma,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to willingly take on this villainous role myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still soft-balling it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man that Ozu had brought in as an adviser
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seemed to have known Jougasaki-senpai for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Ozu schemed to his fullest extent to shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet more and more libelous scenes of his discordant private life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu was like a kid in a candy factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,continuously manipulating the film to deviate from reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the exposé film became nothing more than a personal attack film.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should try going this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Documentaries are deliberate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, let's keep going on this, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's sure looking like this will be an epoch-making work, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh and by the way, please only credit yourself, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I left the editing room and walked aimlessly around Kiyamachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the overhang of someone's house
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was caught by an old woman who emitted a suspiciously ghoulish aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unplaceable aura was persuasive, and thinking logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was no way that the fortunetelling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of a creature who emits such an aura could be anything but spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is a face of extreme impatience… You are unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that you are not in a situation that you believe suits you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can sense your fiercely earnest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly did I tip my hat to the old woman's keen insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I sense there is an opportunity you can't let pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in an excellent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know what that means…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is always dangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must grab this opportunity and act on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I've heard this before…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do not…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will walk this life as now, ever unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 2,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you raise your prices?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the viewer think is best?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spreading around emotions that can move a large number of viewers is basic etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hollywood system is the best in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad your proposal wasn't accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But movies are things everyone should see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you make things you like that make no sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you want to show them to the other people, at least keep a minimum of etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are you wasting the viewer's precious time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's basically like showing you masturbating to the other people! I couldn't stand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck, my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, he's scary…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director! I've been searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so my determination to push forward
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and create and libelous film against Jougasaki-senpai was renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Below my feet ran the Takase River,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just as shallow as all the mass-produced independent films Jougasaki-senpai ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards I returned to the editing room,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and on the morning of the fourth day,\N after three days of editing without sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally completed the worthless documentary which one could say
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HBCBCBC&}Finished
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the culmination of my two prior years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a screening. Please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your chance is during the staff introductions before they show the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head to the projector room then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This movie was created by the hard work of everyone in Misogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really put our all into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that you all will enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we start, let me introduce the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ozu-kun, who helped with the sound recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing both sides are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next we have Akashi-san, who was in charge of the 3D and visual effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Akashi-san during Jougasaki-senpai's shoot at Mt. Yoshida the previous year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was one year younger than me and in the engineering department,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she was hired on staff for her technical skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always meticulous, with never an equipment mishap,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she gained the trust of the other staff, but as she was not one to mince words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seemed there was a distance between her and the people in her class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her sharp tongue, she held her own against Jougasaki-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and although he took an interest in her chilly, intelligent demeanor (and her boobs),
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he never spoke with her, fearful his charismatic flair would be damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san, you sure are fair skinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, fair-skinned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of people with fairer skin than me, so on what basis do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With such a resolute denial and then cross-examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no man ever dared speak with her after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:15:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent off a fiery cheer of "Akashi-san, you just keep doing things your own way!" in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You created another idiotic movie…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you watch such a worthless film.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was definitely worthless but I didn't hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we will start the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy it to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H7061C9&\3c&HC5CED7&\bord1.5\be3\fad(200,0)}"Alexander"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe we should call it off…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring myself to do it with Akashi-san here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\N What happened to your pride as a filmmaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you're on their crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having fun, Alexander?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking will not clear my mind, Ptolemaeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm definitely a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut off the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, didn't he realize this was recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a camera on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are those his?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?\N I barely have enough money to eat, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me… A wall of boobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is this non-fiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If so then… wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie, this is all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop it, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san, you're very pretty again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change your clothes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? We'll smoke him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really fast at running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't like it when things get complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to stop hanging out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After forcing me to do all that, that's quite a thing for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, someone is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You created yet another idiotic movie…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't stop the screening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The viewers found it interesting, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jougasaki-san's faction is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad the people watching had a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he'd call entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I preferred your earlier films.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one was of questionable character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever… It was a hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you haven't kept your promise yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, hurry up and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, now, Akashi-san, fare thee well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not be fooled by Jougasaki's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I seriously look like a fool to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I left behind the site of my unproductive, agonizing struggle over the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I returned to the boarding house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone had sloppily eaten the Castella that Ozu had brought me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason I was tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like my reason had crumbled to pieces like that Castella.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that my next film would be about true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true love film?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love romance where two people tied by fate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would overcome their positions, ages, and even sexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like it's going to turn into something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go, Akashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I squished it… I s-squished it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I am not fond of moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are called Mochiguman, and they come in sets of five, but I have lost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not! As this Earth is round, you are sure to meet once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you'd like, I'll help search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you make that movie a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise? So that's it…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is always dangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…but I didn't hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away with your dreams. That's what I kept telling myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no confidence in that I could comprehend a woman who could understand my selfish movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}And so I tried watching my latest, unfinished film.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shake off the feeling of regret
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for choosing the movie circle "Misogi" in front of that fateful clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had joined some other circle, like for instance the human flight circle "Birdman",
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have surely spent quite a different two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will always haunt me so, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way I show my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it to yourself!
